#originalTopic=Debate:_Single-payer_universal_health_care
 Public health care is good; it just receives more scrutiny/criticism Public health care systems receive more scrutiny by the public because they are publicly accountable. This often gives the impression that these systems are worse. But, this impression is simply a bi-product of the higher level of scrutiny these systems receive. 
